            <title>[HBASE-10208] Add split keys and region location related API in HTable to HTableInterface as well</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10208</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;These are APIs related to split keys avaiable in HTable same can be to HTI&lt;br/&gt;
getStartKeys()&lt;br/&gt;
getEndKeys()&lt;br/&gt;
getStartEndKeys()&lt;br/&gt;
getSplitKeys() - New&lt;br/&gt;
and 3 more APIs related to find region location when we specify row also can be added to HTI&lt;br/&gt;
getRegionLocation(final String row)&lt;br/&gt;
getRegionLocation(final byte [] row)&lt;br/&gt;
getRegionLocation(final byte [] row, boolean reload)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
